job_name: HackerRank (YC S11) is Hiring a Senior Software Engineer Fullstack
hiring_description:
At HackerRank, our mission is to change the world to value skills over pedigree. Thousands of companies use our AI-powered platform to hire next-gen developers based on what they can do, not just what’s on their resume. We’ve powered 300M+ code runs and built a global community of 26M+ developers.

We’ve entered a new era of software development where humans and AI build together. This changes everything- from how developers grow to how companies hire and upskill tech talent. We’re embracing this shift head-on and reinventing our products to meet the moment.

We’re a high-performing, mission-driven team that truly, madly, deeply cares about what we do. We don’t see velocity and quality as tradeoffs; both matter. If you take pride in high-impact work and thrive in a driven team, HackerRank is where you belong.
